          "component_id": "talent",
          "data": {
            "list": [
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Attaque normale</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 2 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.85)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">DGT physiques.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/26b9736a2d14fc4162b2448963f45695_6687420343891246913.png",
                "id": "talent20207",
                "key": "Escrime ancienne des nuages",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 1,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 2,
                    "point_type": "black"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Escrime ancienne des nuages"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Compétence élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Invoque un </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">héraut de givre</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/2575ddfaacc7015ebab2d17fba4593ea_892247457484980513.png",
                "id": "talent81324",
                "key": "Arcane d'Adepte : Héraut de givre",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Arcane d'Adepte : Héraut de givre"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Déchaînement élémentaire</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 3 pts de</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">DGT Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">et crée un</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">talisman de fortune</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Talisman de fortune</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">État de déploiement</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Lorsque votre personnage a utilisé une capacité :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> Si ses PV ne sont pas au maximum, soigne le personnage pour 2 pts.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisation :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> 3</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/900dec327166a00218479cf8616072fc_7727088947986640336.png",
                "id": "talent58041",
                "key": "Arcane d'Adepte : Talisman sacré",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "cryo"
                  },
                  {
                    "point_count": 3,
                    "point_type": "recharge"
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "Arcane d'Adepte : Talisman sacré"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 215, 128)\">Invocation</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Phase finale</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\"> : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Inflige 1 pt de </span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">DGT Cryo</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.45)\">.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Nombre d'utilisations : </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">3</span></p><p><span style=\"color: #FFFFFF\">Lorsque cette invocation est sur le terrain et que Qiqi a utilisé une attaque normale :</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\"> Soigne votre personnage ayant subi le plus de DGT pour 1 pt.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/db13288db6b90ec33f8adc2656d2019f_6816683215164966418.png",
                "id": "talent55139",
                "key": "Héraut de givre",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/971b05c02dd20b662457e953c3c1ce93_4334611992101808221.png",
                "title": "Héraut de givre"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Applique l'élément Cryo et peut déclencher les réactions élémentaires :</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 153, 153)\">Pyro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Fonte </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +2</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 172, 255)\">Électro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Supraconduction </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et inflige 1 pt de DGT de perforation à tous les personnages adverses autres que la cible</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">[</span><span style=\"color: rgb(153, 255, 255)\">Cryo </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">+ </span><span style=\"color: rgb(128, 192, 255)\">Hydro</span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">] </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">Gel </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">: DGT actuels +1 et immobilise la cible pendant la manche actuelle (Peut être annulé en avance en subissant des DGT physiques ou Pyro, mais DGT +2)</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/4bcc4b82a9d7ee22770f60afa54e9919_4936318775097309118.png",
                "id": "talent34269",
                "key": "DGT Cryo",
                "materials": [],
                "points": [
                  {
                    "point_count": 0,
                    "point_type": ""
                  }
                ],
                "talent_img": "",
                "title": "DGT Cryo"
              },
              {
                "attributes": [],
                "desc": "<p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">DGT physiques</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Les DGT physiques n'appliquent aucun élément et ne peuvent pas non plus déclencher de réactions élémentaires.</span></p><p></p><p><strong><span style=\"color: rgb(236, 229, 216)\">Nombre d'utilisations</span></strong></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Après le déclenchement de l'effet de cette carte, 1 de ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">est consommée.</span></p><p><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">Une carte est immédiatement défaussée une fois toutes ses </span><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255)\">utilisations </span><span style=\"color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.65)\">épuisées.</span></p>",
                "icon_url": "https://upload-static.hoyoverse.com/hoyolab-wiki/2023/08/15/35653081/245c229cf6f7364c7c9a7aea3db1a1ad_1306080551506039458.png",
